{"tid":1402240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好意思，唔好再話前線冇鬼","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T15:56:27.000Z","uid":28994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"88058cbaf2057a644c760a106f6c5c0383852643","tid":1402240,"uid":28994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:56:27.000Z","msg":"冇鬼既話點會有便衣<br />\n更加唔會有水刮隊長啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警黑勾結都做得出<br />\n仲以為冇鬼會唔會太天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係死黑警既話梗係想你留低比班狗出火啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我地根本冇方法去捉鬼<br />\n一捉鬼又有機會搞到分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地唔應該咁易比人帶風向</span><br />\n希望各位抗爭者可以跟自己諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要快閃既就繼續快閃<br />\n見到有人要死守既話冇問題<br />\n放底你既尊重就夠人唔洗留<br />\n唔好比黑警利用一齊黎一齊走呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前線唔係得留守一招<br />\n記住be water, hit &amp; run 一樣可以係前線決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]}